description:
DPN is the digital token symbol of the Industrial Blockchain program “DIPNET”, which can give various combination, like Lego does, to the industrial manufacturing in the future.

Every production unit (which German calls it Industry 4.0 component) completes the order from the industrial chain to reorganize and show quick reaction to the changes in the external market by taking advantage in the Distributed Intelligent Production Network (DIPNET), which is constructed by Industrial Cloud and Industrial Blockchain Technology, and growing itself in the thousands of smart contract paradigms in the DIPNET network.

Industrial society will no longer be full of cumbersome machines, but will be much faster and much easier, and the future industry will not only be much more lucrative, but also looks cooler than ever.
name: Dipnet
